Package uk.ac.man.jb.pct.data

Interface Summary
I_ClassifierStatistics I_ClassifierStatistics provides an interface for providing the statistics needed to describe the accuracy of a classifier.
I_DataFileParser I_DataFileParser, defines an interface specifying the methods needed to read the data files used by the application.
I_DataSet I_DataSet and interface defining the methods used to manipulate a data set.
I_DataSetTransformer I_DataSetTransformer defines methods that can be used to convert I_DataSet objects in to other forms.
I_InputPattern I_InputPattern is an interface that defines the operations to be applied to input patterns read in from input files.
I_OutputResults I_OutputResults, specifies the methods that can be used to write classification results to output files.
 

Class Summary

DataSetTransformer DataSetTransformer.
InputPattern Class representing an individual input pattern.
OutputResults OutputResults, a class used to write classifications to an output file.
PatternFileProcessor Class that processes a file containing input patterns, and returns the data as DataSet instances.
 

Enum Summary
I_InputPattern.DataType The different types of data an input pattern may contain.
